channel.description: Once you have your material selected, we can start choosing how we want each shape to be cut. Image On the left of the screen will show all individual objects in the workspace. Click on the object you wish to change the settings of. Image Cut Options A menu will appear, with various options. First letâ€™s look at the top menu. Each of the options on the top menu will cut the object in a different way.
